metadata.name: Bon appetit!
metadata.description:
She is a Maine Coon Cat girl.
She works energetically at a seafood restaurant that prides itself on its lobster!
The sea breeze shakes her proud fur.
You too can enjoy the delicious lobster at this restaurant!

***
[ Maine Coon (cat) ]
Maine Coons are native to the state of Maine in New England.
Maine is known for its lobsters!
That's the inspiration for her setting.
